<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/common/reset.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/common/pay_info.min.css">
  <script src="../../js/flexible.min.js"></script>
  <title>已拒绝</title>
</head>

<body>
  <div id="pay">
    <div class="form-group">
      <div class="form-item">
        <div class="text">拒绝人</div>
        <div class="value">中俄混血儿</div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-item">
        <div class="text">拒绝金额</div>
        <div class="value">
          <i class="letter">¥</i>
          <span class="price">729</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-item">
        <div class="text">拒绝人</div>
        <div class="value">2019-10-25 10:28:49</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="content-box">
        <div class="title">拒绝人二维码</div>
        <div class="content">
          <img class="content__img" src="../../images/userInfo/test-qrcode.png" alt="">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="content-box">
        <div class="title">拒绝原因</div>
        <div class="content">
          <div class="content-remark">
            开始对接发了刷卡的缴费来看撒旦教发雷克萨大姐夫拉萨的减
            肥雷克萨大姐夫离开撒打飞机了撒旦教离开时发动机离开水电
            费就。
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="content-box">
        <div class="title">打款凭证</div>
        <div class="content">
          <img class="content__img" src="../../images/pay/test-pay.png" alt="">
          <div class="content-again">
            <input type="file" id="again_upload">
            <span class="again-text">更换凭证</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="content-box">
        <div class="title">打款备注</div>
        <div class="content">
          <textarea class="content__textarea" placeholder="请填写备注"></textarea>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group mt20">
      <div class="form-item">
        <div class="text">提交时间</div>
        <div class="value">2019-10-25 10:28:49</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <button class="submit-btn center-block" type="button">重新提交</button>
  </div>
</body>

<script src="../../js/jquery.min.2.1.1.js"></script>
<script src="../../js/common.js"></script>

